"{\"uid\": \"metro.co.uk-2024-07-31-athletes-eating-packed-lunches-olympics-one-food-really-want-21328207\", \"noun_phrases\": [{\"sentence\": \"For many of us, a packed lunch will likely consist of last night's leftovers, or a sad sandwich andpacket of crisps.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 116, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 12, \"to\": 14}, {\"ngram\": \"a packed lunch\", \"from\": 16, \"to\": 30}, {\"ngram\": \"last night's leftovers\", \"from\": 54, \"to\": 76}, {\"ngram\": \"a sad sandwich andpacket\", \"from\": 81, \"to\": 105}, {\"ngram\": \"crisps\", \"from\": 109, \"to\": 115}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So it might surprise many to hear thatTeam GB's sports starshave been tucking into a 'packed lunch' most nights for dinner at theOlympic VillageinParis.\", \"from\": 118, \"to\": 270, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 161, \"end\": 163, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9999983019766524, \"rank\": 1.5677245809181355e-06, \"text\": \"GB\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a 'packed lunch' most nights\", \"from\": 201, \"to\": 229}, {\"ngram\": \"dinner\", \"from\": 234, \"to\": 240}, {\"ngram\": \"theOlympic VillageinParis\", \"from\": 244, \"to\": 269}]}, {\"sentence\": \"According to Andy Anson, the British Olympic Association's chief executive, the food at the Village has been 'inadequate' meaning that athletes have been getting their meals elsewhere.\", \"from\": 272, \"to\": 456, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 285, \"end\": 295, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Anson\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Andy Anson\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Anson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Anson\"}, {\"begin\": 301, \"end\": 328, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Olympic_Association\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"British Olympic Association\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Olympic_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Olympic_Association\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the food\", \"from\": 348, \"to\": 356}, {\"ngram\": \"the Village\", \"from\": 360, \"to\": 371}, {\"ngram\": \"'inadequate' meaning\", \"from\": 381, \"to\": 401}, {\"ngram\": \"athletes\", \"from\": 407, \"to\": 415}, {\"ngram\": \"their meals\", \"from\": 434, \"to\": 445}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Andy said a 'dramatic improvement' was needed when it came to food, as there had not been enough protein to go around.\", \"from\": 458, \"to\": 576, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Andy\", \"from\": 458, \"to\": 462}, {\"ngram\": \"a 'dramatic improvement\", \"from\": 468, \"to\": 491}, {\"ngram\": \"food\", \"from\": 520, \"to\": 524}, {\"ngram\": \"enough protein\", \"from\": 548, \"to\": 562}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He also claimed thatraw meat had been served to athletes.\", \"from\": 577, \"to\": 634, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"thatraw meat\", \"from\": 593, \"to\": 605}, {\"ngram\": \"athletes\", \"from\": 625, \"to\": 633}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Instead of eating at the Village, British athletes have been heading to the Performance Lodge 20 minutes away in Clichy.\", \"from\": 636, \"to\": 756, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 670, \"end\": 677, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9931634570336555, \"rank\": 0.006777699232360235, \"text\": \"British\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}, {\"begin\": 749, \"end\": 755, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clichy-sous-Bois\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.7073218449894643e-16, \"text\": \"Clichy\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clichy-sous-Bois\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clichy-sous-Bois\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Village\", \"from\": 657, \"to\": 668}, {\"ngram\": \"the Performance Lodge\", \"from\": 708, \"to\": 729}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This is a space for Team GB where they can train, rest, recover, and prepare for competition.\", \"from\": 757, \"to\": 850, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a space\", \"from\": 765, \"to\": 772}, {\"ngram\": \"Team GB\", \"from\": 777, \"to\": 784}, {\"ngram\": \"competition\", \"from\": 838, \"to\": 849}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'The athletes are not just going there to eat their lunch, they are packing meals for their dinner as they do not want to go into the athlete restaurant to eat,' Andy adds.\", \"from\": 852, \"to\": 1024, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The athletes\", \"from\": 853, \"to\": 865}, {\"ngram\": \"their lunch\", \"from\": 898, \"to\": 909}, {\"ngram\": \"meals\", \"from\": 928, \"to\": 933}, {\"ngram\": \"their dinner\", \"from\": 938, \"to\": 950}, {\"ngram\": \"the athlete restaurant\", \"from\": 982, \"to\": 1004}, {\"ngram\": \"Andy\", \"from\": 1014, \"to\": 1018}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's not been revealed what exactly the team have been putting in their lunchboxes, but it's likely they will have been stocking up on everything the village has been in short supply of, including chicken, eggs, and carbohydrates.\", \"from\": 1026, \"to\": 1256, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the team\", \"from\": 1062, \"to\": 1070}, {\"ngram\": \"their lunchboxes\", \"from\": 1092, \"to\": 1108}, {\"ngram\": \"everything\", \"from\": 1161, \"to\": 1171}, {\"ngram\": \"the village\", \"from\": 1172, \"to\": 1183}, {\"ngram\": \"short supply\", \"from\": 1196, \"to\": 1208}, {\"ngram\": \"chicken\", \"from\": 1223, \"to\": 1230}, {\"ngram\": \"eggs\", \"from\": 1232, \"to\": 1236}, {\"ngram\": \"carbohydrates\", \"from\": 1242, \"to\": 1255}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And some will be eating a hefty amount, as Olympic 200m freestyle champion Tom Dean recently toldThe Independentthat he consumes 6,000 to 7,000 calories per day, with two big breakfasts, a big lunch, a snack, a large meal, and then another snack before bed.\", \"from\": 1258, \"to\": 1515, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1333, \"end\": 1341, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Dean_(swimmer)\", \"score\": 0.9999936593363623, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Tom Dean\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Dean_(swimmer)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Dean_(swimmer)\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a hefty amount\", \"from\": 1282, \"to\": 1296}, {\"ngram\": \"6,000 to 7,000 calories\", \"from\": 1387, \"to\": 1410}, {\"ngram\": \"day\", \"from\": 1415, \"to\": 1418}, {\"ngram\": \"two big breakfasts\", \"from\": 1425, \"to\": 1443}, {\"ngram\": \"a big lunch\", \"from\": 1445, \"to\": 1456}, {\"ngram\": \"a snack\", \"from\": 1458, \"to\": 1465}, {\"ngram\": \"a large meal\", \"from\": 1467, \"to\": 1479}, {\"ngram\": \"then another snack\", \"from\": 1485, \"to\": 1503}, {\"ngram\": \"bed\", \"from\": 1511, \"to\": 1514}]}, {\"sentence\": \"His first breakfast typically includes oats with peanut butter, banana, fruits and honey, which gives him around 1,200 calories to begin the day.\", \"from\": 1517, \"to\": 1662, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"His first breakfast\", \"from\": 1517, \"to\": 1536}, {\"ngram\": \"oats\", \"from\": 1556, \"to\": 1560}, {\"ngram\": \"peanut butter\", \"from\": 1566, \"to\": 1579}, {\"ngram\": \"banana\", \"from\": 1581, \"to\": 1587}, {\"ngram\": \"fruits\", \"from\": 1589, \"to\": 1595}, {\"ngram\": \"honey\", \"from\": 1600, \"to\": 1605}, {\"ngram\": \"around 1,200 calories\", \"from\": 1623, \"to\": 1644}, {\"ngram\": \"the day\", \"from\": 1654, \"to\": 1661}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He then follows this up with scrambled eggs, a bagel and avocado.\", \"from\": 1663, \"to\": 1728, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"scrambled eggs\", \"from\": 1692, \"to\": 1706}, {\"ngram\": \"a bagel\", \"from\": 1708, \"to\": 1715}, {\"ngram\": \"avocado\", \"from\": 1720, \"to\": 1727}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Many of his fellow British athletes will also be starting their day with porridge, as Philipp W\\u00fcrz, head of food and beverages at the Games, revealed it was the most requested food by Team GB ahead of the Olympics.\", \"from\": 1730, \"to\": 1944, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1749, \"end\": 1756, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9931634570336555, \"rank\": 0.006777699232360235, \"text\": \"British\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}, {\"begin\": 1914, \"end\": 1921, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"score\": 0.9955338884196312, \"rank\": 0.0044491559010384745, \"text\": \"Team GB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"their day\", \"from\": 1788, \"to\": 1797}, {\"ngram\": \"porridge\", \"from\": 1803, \"to\": 1811}, {\"ngram\": \"Philipp W\\u00fcrz\", \"from\": 1816, \"to\": 1828}, {\"ngram\": \"head\", \"from\": 1830, \"to\": 1834}, {\"ngram\": \"food\", \"from\": 1838, \"to\": 1842}, {\"ngram\": \"beverages\", \"from\": 1847, \"to\": 1856}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 1860, \"to\": 1869}, {\"ngram\": \"the most requested food\", \"from\": 1887, \"to\": 1910}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 1931, \"to\": 1943}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This is likely because it's considered a 'superfood' by many experts.\", \"from\": 1946, \"to\": 2015, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a 'superfood\", \"from\": 1985, \"to\": 1997}, {\"ngram\": \"many experts\", \"from\": 2002, \"